00:37:00.960 --> 00:37:03.079
on what was happening around him

00:37:03.079 --> 00:37:05.559
or what was happening to him.

00:37:05.559 --> 00:37:07.360
From a heart filled with faith,

00:37:07.360 --> 00:37:12.360
