00:37:12.360 --> 00:37:14.559
That is why Paul was joyful

00:37:14.559 --> 00:37:18.760
despite any injustice or anxiety that he experienced.

00:37:19.659 --> 00:37:21.760
Always rejoice, he said.

00:37:21.760 --> 00:37:23.659
Again, rejoice.

00:37:24.559 --> 00:37:27.960
What will help us to apply these inspired words?

00:37:27.960 --> 00:37:30.460
